OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPerry was in a good place, 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FFriends creator says       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Matthew Perry was happy and chipper    
OL,6, when Friends co-creator Marta Kauffman 
OL,7, spoke to him two weeks ago, she says.  
OL,9,FTributes have been paid to Perry, who  
OL,10,Fplayed Chandler in the TV sitcom, since
OL,11,Fhis death, on Saturday, aged 54.       
OL,13,FKauffman told the National Broadcasting
OL,14,FCompany's (NBC) Today programme their  
OL,15,Flast chat had been "great".            
OL,17,F"He didn't seem weighed down by        
OL,18,Fanything," she said. "He was in a      
OL,19,Freally good place, which is why this   
OL,20,Fseems so unfair."                      
